Version 2.26:
- [!] 17 Sep 2008, Arsitov - Bug (0051040): Spaces at the beginning and the end of a product option were handled incorrectly. Fixed.

Version 2.25:
- [!] 13 Dec 2007, Alien - Bug (0029865): Product options surcharges didn't take into account wholesale prices. Fixed.
- [!] 27 Nov 2007, Alien - Bug (0029946): Prices with product options were calculated incorrectly in bulk shopping mode, if wholesale price of this product had been set for Amount=1. Fixed. 

Version 2.24:
- [!] 25 Sep 2007, Osipov - Bug (0026460): Global product options were not created for products imported using CSV files. Fixed.
- [+] 29 Aug 2007, Alien - Improvement (0022413): The list of categories on the Global product options page is sped up.

Version 2.23:
- [+] 12 Apr 2007, Sheriff - Improvement (0017395): The module templates were corrected to be W3C compatible.
- [!] 15 Jan 2007, Sheriff - Bug (0015390): When a product option contained a quotation mark and was added for tracking (when the "InventoryTracking" module was active) the option name was always truncated. Fixed.
- [!] 25 Dec 2006, Osipov - Improvement (0014786): Now module can handle large numbers of product options used in exceptions (Excluded option combinations).

Version 2.22:
- [!] 22 Aug 2006, Sheriff - Bug (0011157): A refactoring of the PHP code (in the procedure of taxes calculation) was done to increase compartibility with WholesaleTrading and PromotionTools modules.
- [!] 22 Aug 2006, Sheriff - Bug (0010284): A few typos were fixed.

Version 2.21:
- [+] 17 Mar 2006, Sheriff - Improvement: Compatibility with the future versions (2.2+) of LiteCommerce software and PHP 5+ was added.
- [!] 06 Mar 2006, Osipov - Bug (0006040): An unnecessary "+" sign could be displayed next to option price modifiers in the 'Options' drop-down box on the 'Product details' page. Fixed.
- [!] 02 Feb 2006, Sheriff - Bug (0005733): When a product was cloned the JavaScript enhancements code was not cloned. Fixed.

Version 2.20:
- [!] 23 Dec 2005, Sheriff - Bug (0005382): When global product options were set on several categories and some products were listed simultaneously in those categories (MultiCategories is on), taking one of the categories out of the list to which the product options applied was clearing the options for those products. Fixed.
- [+] 23 Dec 2005, Sheriff - Improvement (0005376): In global product options' definitions categories to which the global product options apply are now displayed at the top of the list of categories.
- [!] 22 Dec 2005, Sheriff - Bug (0005346): When global product options were set on several categories and some product first listed in one of the categories was being added to another category to which the same global product options applied, the options for that product were duplicated. Fixed.
- [!] 27 Oct 2005, Sheriff - Bug (0004644): Problem exporting/importing global product options containing singly quote symbol. Fixed.
- [+] 13 Oct 2005, Sheriff - Improvement (0004455): Option-modified prices now include taxes when 'product prices already include tax' parameter is on. 
- [!] 15 Sep 2005, Sheriff - Bug (0004169): Global product options containing single quote symbol could not be deleted. Fixed.

Version 2.19:
- [+] 01 Sep 2005, Oley - Improvement: The module reference manual has been rewritten from scratch.
- [+] 25 Aug 2005, Sheriff - Improvement: New interface for excluding non-existent product option combinations has been introduced.
- [+] 22 Aug 2005, Sheriff - Improvement: The outlook of all dialogues concerned with product options were redesigned to one common style. All product options' related dialogues have been redesigned to attain the matching look and feel.
- [+] 22 Aug 2005, Asd - Improvement: Enhanced compatibility with the WholesaleTrading and InventoryTracking modules.
- [+] 10 Aug 2005, Asd, Sheriff - Improvement (0003659): New logic of "Global Product Options" implementation has been introduced, fixing multiple inconsistencies.

Version 2.18:
- [!] 01 Jul 2005, Sheriff - Bug (0003677): The "out of stock" message was not shown when "track without product options" functionality was enabled and the product was out of stock (when the "InventoryTracking" module was active). Fixed.
- [+] 30 May 2005, Sheriff - Improvement: Templates were modified to make them compatible with the new version of the "ProductAdviser" module.

Version 2.17:
- [!] 20 May 2005, Sheriff - Bug: When admin changed order status from "queued" to "processed" and "InventoryTracking" module handled the situation it caused a crash of the template engine (one template was omitted). Fixed.
- [!] 18 May 2005, Sheriff - Bug: Adding a new product options exception after modifying product options occasionally caused PHP code to crash. Fixed. 
- [+] 18 May 2005, Sheriff - Improvement: Minor JS-code optimization was made for enhanced compatibility with the new versions (2.10+) of the "WholesaleTrading" module. 
- [!] 28 Apr 2005, Sheriff - Bug: Mandatory 'Option class' field was not being checked for an empty value. Fixed.

Version 2.16:
- [!] 25 Apr 2005, Sheriff - Bug: Categories were not checked for identical names which caused PHP code to crash. Fixed.

Version 2.15:
- [!] 07 Mar 2005, Asd - Bug: The compiled code/templates cache was not cleaned up during the module uninstallation. Fixed.
- [+] 05 Mar 2005, Asd - Improvement: The ability to interact with the new versions (2.4+) of the "InventoryTracking" modules was added. Now all inventory tracking data will be recalculated automatically when admin changes/deletes a product option class or a product options list.
- [+] 04 Mar 2005, Asd - Improvement: The ability to clone product options of a product during the cloning of the product. Now admin can enable/disable this feature in the "Module ProductOptions settings" dialogue - there is the option "Clone product options when product is cloned".

Version 2.14:
- [!] 01 Feb 2005, Sheriff - Bug: The calculation of the price value with a percent surcharge was wrong (new "VATed" price calculation began to affect the absolute surcharge only). Fixed.

Version 2.13:
- [!] 31 Jan 2005, Sheriff - Bug: The "price surcharge" value was calculated without rounding off when a product with an "included VAT" price was added to the cart. Fixed. 
- [!] 31 Jan 2005, Sheriff - Bug: The tax value was calculated in a wrong way (when a product with an "included VAT" price was added to the cart, the resulting tax value was calculated according to an already "VATed" price). Fixed.

Version 2.12:
- [!] 31 Jan 2005, Sheriff - Bug: The "price surcharge" value was calculated in a wrong way (when a product with an "included VAT" price was added to the cart, the resulting price value was different for the same products with absolute surcharge and percent surcharge). Fixed.

Version 2.11:
 - [+] 28 Dec 2004, Sheriff - Improvement: The ability to choose if you want to show the actual price/weight or the price/weight modifier is added.
 
Version 2.10:
 - [!] 22 Dec 2004, Sheriff - Bug: Under certain conditions the behavior of some functions was changed on PHP 4.3.10 with some Zend enhancements ('unset()' function, for example). Fixed (additional verification was added).
